    "body": "I received an error when I tried to run the code in the spack views docs: https://spack.readthedocs.io/en/latest/workflows.html?highlight=loads%20exclude#fine-grain-control\r\n\r\n### Expected Result\r\n\r\n```\r\nspack view symlink --dependencies yes --exclude appsy appsy\r\n<generating view>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Actual Result\r\n\r\n```\r\nspack view symlink --dependencies yes --exclude appsy appsy\r\n==> Error: unrecognized arguments: --dependencies --exclude\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe documented command should be:\r\n`spack view --dependencies yes --exclude appsy symlink /path/to/MYVIEW/ appsy`\r\n\r\nShould the course of action be to change the documentation or the command?  Presumably the changes to the command were intentional and the docs are just out of date?",
